ENUGU – Tragedy occurred on Saturday in Oruku community, Nka­nu-East Local Gov­ernment Area in Enugu State, when unidentified men shot dead the traditional ruler of the community, Igwe Emman­uel Chidebere Mba. The incident, which threw the community into mourn­ing, led to protest by aggrieved members of the community while houses and property believed to belong to those be­hind the ugly incident, were set ablaze. It was alleged that some men, who dressed in a po­lice uniform, drove into the community in an SUV on Saturday evening while the monarch was having a meet­ing with his subjects at the town hall. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! An eye witness account told reporters that the said po­licemen demanded to see the traditional ruler and when the monarch was identified, one of the men shot at him and he fell down in a pool of his blood. According to him, there was pandemonium in the community as a result of the incident as residents scam­pered for safety Bishop Kukah’s Allegations Against Buhari Unfounded – BMO Olugbo Greets Subjects At Christmas, Exudes Hope Of Better Nigeria In 2021 It was further revealed that the monarch was rushed to the hospital for treatment but was confirmed dead by a doc­tor at the National Orthopedic Hospital. It was learnt that corpse of the late monarch has been deposited at National Ortho­pedic Hospital Mortuary. INDEPENDENT learnt that over six houses and sev­eral vehicles have been de­stroyed in Oruku communi­ty while some other buildings were on fire as of the time of filling this report When contacted, the Pub­lic Relations Officer of Enugu State Police Command, Daniel Ndukwe, said the situation in Oruku community has been brought under control and the Commissioner of Police has directed a full-scale inves­tigation into the incident, and anyone found wanting should be arrested and prosecuted. He further called on people of the community to remain calm and eschew acts capa­ble of further breaching the peace in the area, as anyone caught will be made to face the full weight of the law. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION